# Unity Agent Bridge product repository ignores

# .NET build outputs
**/bin/
**/obj/
TestResults/
*.trx
*.coverage
*.coveragexml

# Node/npm dependencies and logs
**/node_modules/
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
pnpm-debug.log*
package-lock.json

# Unity-generated files if this package is opened in a Unity project context
Library/
Logs/
Temp/
Obj/
Build/
Builds/
UserSettings/
MemoryCaptures/
Recordings/
*.suo
*.user
*.userprefs
*.pidb
*.booproj
*.svd
*.pdb
*.mdb
*.opendb
*.VC.db

# IDE/editor state
.vs/
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo

# OS files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
Desktop.ini

# Agent Bridge local runtime state
.unitymcp/

# Package-contained published executables are generated release artifacts.
com.unitymcp.agent-bridge/Tools~/UnityAgentBridge/cli/out/**

com.unitymcp.agent-bridge/Tools~/UnityAgentBridge/roslyn-execution/out/**
